<br>
Mana regen is KEY, which is why our epic and flowing thoughts items do a LOT more than you might think just by looking at the numbers.<br>
<br>
Epic, +3 mana/tick=30 mana/minute<br>
<br>
Now, this means that if you are low on mana, you can root the mob, sit down, and with the epic effect up, in many cases you can get enough mana back to re-root, but also to possibly nuke the mob down.  I'm not sure what the NORMAL mana regen rate is, but between epic, and one or more flowing thoughts items, you WILL find you can nuke a bit more.  <br>
 <p>Targonis Manastorm<br>
Level 58 Wizard<br>
The Nameless Server<br>
